Statistics of patients with COVID-19 for February 20 / News
Over the past day, February 20, 13,562 new confirmed cases of the coronavirus disease were recorded in Ukraine. Of them, 1,254 children and 151 medical workers were infected.
Source:
Ministry of Health
At the same time, the number of hospitalized patients also decreased over the past day: 1,886 people compared to 3,172 patients who were admitted to the hospital a day earlier.
